The '''Academy of Fire''' is a building in the [[Veteran Barracks]] category. It is used to recruit [[Fire Mage]]s.

== Production ==
The Academy of Fire produces one [[Fire Mage]] every 15 seconds. It consumes 50 [[Wheat]] per cycle.

